>\n餵畜生又得<br />\n<br />\n渣埋入面異黃酮，當保健品賣又得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後最後最後，仲可以吊高來賣比支那賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點會用唔晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T23:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}